Jurgen Klopp announced his departure from Borussia Dortmund on Wednesday . 
  The German manager will leave the Bundesliga club at the end of the season . 
  Manuel Pellegrini could be on his way out of Manchester City after a poor season . 
  Dietmar Hamann believes Klopp would be the ideal fit for the job . 
  Klopp won the Bundesliga title twice during his time at Dortmund . 
  He has been linked with Real Madrid and Manchester City . 
 